    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. can you get more specific with the details? like, give me some concrete examples of the \"classic\" dress codes for meetings and maybe some tips on communication styles or dining etiquette that someone should follow to make sure they come across as elite and professional anywhere in the world.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
